method.name: REX1

reference.ref: Akgobek, O., Aydin, Y. S., Oztemel, E., & Aksoy, M. S. (2006). A new algorithm for automatic knowledge acquisition in inductive learning. Knowledge-based systems, 19(6), 388-395.

generalDescription.type: Classification model by inductive rule learning.
generalDescription.objective: To determine a set of rules that discards the pitfalls encountered in the RULES family algorithms, introducing the use of the entropy value.
generalDescription.howWork: REX1 extracts rules analyzing correlations between class and attributes values, by means of (reformulated) entropy.

parameterSpec.param: ENTROPIA: Entropy calculation equation to be used (see reference. ENTROPIA=1: Eq. (3); ENTROPIA=2: Eq. (4))

method.example:
